                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc>
                          The opening prayers: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ።</foreign> and the the first part of the <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነአኵትከ፡</foreign>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
